t elementor-headline-text-wrapper\">Advantage<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/h3>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-28bbbaf elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"28bbbaf\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Whether you are looking to reach old customers, or find new ones, IFR is an ideal venue in which to promote your business to a premium readership:<\/p><ul><li>Helijet passengers are a well-defined audience of affluent professionals. Advertisers can achieve a variety of marketing objectives by targeting this desirable readership of influential leaders and decision makers in industry and government.<\/li><li>IFR magazine provides superior editorial content and visual design in a quality product; your business image will be part of the overall reading experience.<\/li><li>As a quarterly magazine, your ad receives prolonged exposure over three months.<\/li><li>IFR is distributed to several luxury hotels and resorts, further increasing your ad\u2019s exposure.<\/li><li>Qualified advertisers receive travel benefits of up to $1,000 on Helijet.<\/li><\/ul>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2a48ce0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"2a48ce0\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-e-type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-11e6845 elementor-widget elementor-widget-button\" data-id=\"11e6845\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-e-type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"button.default\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a class=\"elementor-button elementor-button-link elementor-size-sm\" href=\"\/contact-us\/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-content-wrapper\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span class=\"elementor-button-text\">Book a Consultation<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-elem